2. **Thread Parallelism** (cpu_bound) - Parallelize orders scan across 64 cores → ~14x speedup on remaining work
3. **Bloom Filter Join Pruning** (join) - Eliminate 98% of hash probes in lineitem join → 163ms to ~90ms

